== Spell Strategy ==

=== Early Game ===

* Heal for survival
* Crack/Sizz for groups
* Snooze to control enemies

=== Mid Game ===

* Midheal/Fullheal for healing
* Boom/Kasizz for AoE
* Buff/Kabuff for bosses

=== Late Game ===

* Omniheal for emergencies
* Kafrizzle for single targets
* Kaboom/Kasizzle for groups

=== Boss Fights ===

* Kabuff party defense
* Magic Barrier vs casters
* Fullheal/Omniheal rotation
* Avoid instant death spells

